#ad It's time to show you some behind-the-scenes of the dance club playhouse we are building in partnership with @KinderUS for the #KinderJoy x Barbie “You Can Be Anything Sweepstakes.” We are thrilled to partner with Kinder Joy to inspire families and kids to dream big and pursue their passions through play. To enter, parents can visit kinderjoybarbiesweeps.com or click on the link in our bio by September 17.
 
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. Open only to legal residents of the 48 contiguous United States and DC who are 18 years of age or older with a valid email account as of the date of entry. Sweepstakes begin at 12:00 a.m. ET on 8/25/21 and ends at 11:59 p.m. ET on 9/17/21. Void in Alaska, Hawaii, Puerto Rico and where prohibited. For complete details, see Official Rules available at www.kinderjoybarbiesweeps.com Sponsor: Ferrero U.S.A., Inc., Parsippany, NJ 07054

Who wants to win a fully-decorated, interactive, customized playhouse? #ad @KinderUS is partnering with us to give two families the chance to win a Charmed Playhouse. #KinderJoy's latest treat will include five Barbie characters that help kids imagine all they can be such as a scientist, DJ, baker, athlete and movie director. Please visit kinderjoybarbiesweeps.com or click on the link in our bio to enter the Kinder Joy x Barbie, "You Can Be Anything Sweepstakes." 

NO PURCHASE NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN. Open only to legal residents of the 48 contiguous United States and DC who are 18 years of age or older with a valid email account as of the date of entry.
